# Normalize line endings to LF in the repository and in every working tree.
#
# Without this, a Windows checkout with core.autocrlf=true materializes text
# files as CRLF. That is invisible to most tooling but not to the checks that
# compare files byte-for-byte — db/tools/build-0001.mjs compares migration
# 0001 against the frozen schema, and it reported spurious drift on Windows
# while passing on Linux CI. Pinning eol=lf makes those checks mean the same
# thing everywhere.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary: never touch these.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.pdf binary
*.docx binary
*.ico binary
